you cant blame investors in gold and other 
precious metals right now if they have trouble understanding why 
the federal reserve is so worried about inflation 
traditionally gold has been one of the most reliable ways to 
bet on inflation and thus protect the purchasing power of your 
money from increases in the cost of living 
