temperatures but she declined to give any details the free press 
said the swelling was so bad that doors wouldnt close 
she said the problem stemmed from the material used in making 
the doors rather than the injection molding process which has been 
used in the past for parts no larger than bumpers 
saturn is not experiencing any more preproduction problems 
than normally encountered with the startup of an allnew vehicle 
kay said 
saturn is due to arrive in dealer showrooms on schedule this 
fall she said the free press quoted a source as saying its 
going to be a photo finish theres no doubt in my mind 
