washington apple belt produces an apple that is crisper tastier 
and more durable than red delicious the industry standard since 
the 1920s 
the fujis also are bringing much higher wholesale prices not a 
minor consideration after three consecutive years of poor prices 
that have caused many growers to reassess the heartshaped red 
delicious 
