conspiracy to defraud the government and participating in the 
filing of false excise tax returns 
the kennons operate jenny oil corp oil city enterprises inc 
and mount vernon energy terminals inc the charges against each of 
the kennons carry a maximum penalty of 14 years imprisonment and 
fines totaling 550000 
