decision to block his efforts to acquire all of pathe cinema a 
major french movie and tv producer with a 400film library and a 
chain of about 400 theaters pathe cinema is unrelated to pathe 
communications 
parretti asked the european community commission in brussels to 
overturn french finance minister pierre beregovoys decision to 
block the purchase of pathe cinema he said the decision was 
arbitrary and an abuse of power 
parretti already owns 48 percent of pathe cinema 
